FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772062286
OL,3,CFly-tipping: Farmers facing
OL,4,C'continuous battle' of dumped waste
OL,6,FAs well as the spiralling cost to
OL,7,Ffarmers, fly-tipping in the
OL,8,Fcountryside is a major environmental
OL,9,Fissue prompting calls for tougher
OL,10,Faction from the authorities.
OL,12,FTim Bamford from the Country Land and
OL,13,FBusiness Association said: "It is on
OL,14,Fthe government, the Environment Agency
OL,15,Fand on local authorities to
OL,16,Finvestigate and fundamentally
OL,17,Fprosecute those criminals who are
OL,18,Fdoing this and stop them from doing it
OL,19,Fagain in the future."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
