FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772062286
OL,3,CFly-tipping: Farmers facing
OL,4,C'continuous battle' of dumped waste
OL,6,FNew guidance issued on Wednesday will
OL,7,Fhelp local authorities crack down on
OL,8,Fwaste crime, according to the
OL,9,FGovernment.
OL,11,FCircular Economy Minister, Mary Creagh
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are empowering local
OL,13,Fauthorities to clamp down on waste
OL,14,Fcowboys and restore pride in our local
OL,15,Fareas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,412,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1772062286
OL,3,CFly-tipping: Farmers facing
OL,4,C'continuous battle' of dumped waste
OL,6,F"I share the public's fury at seeing
OL,7,Four streets, parks and fields used as
OL,8,Fdumping grounds. Fly-tippers should
OL,9,Fknow ` if you use your van to trash
OL,10,Four countryside, don't be surprised
OL,11,Fwhen it ends up on the scrapheap."
OL,13,FDefra says councils will be given more
OL,14,Fpowers to seize and crush more
OL,15,Fvehicles used for fly-tipping along
OL,16,Fwith advice on how to take cases to
OL,17,Fcourt.
OL,19,FCouncils are also being urged to name
OL,20,Fand shame culprits on social media.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
